Age Of Deceit - Fallen Angels And The New World Order:

This full length feature titled 'Age of Deceit: Fallen Angels and the New World Order' is a biblical look at the history of fallen angels and the relationship to the New World Order and the New Age Movement.

Topics covered are the fall of mankind, the pre-flood world as Atlantis, the new age through theosophy, the fallen angels and their origin of planting the seeds to society, UFO's, ET's and abduction cases, demonic possession, channeling, and more.  Featured on the video are Chris White and Douglas Hamp.
